<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="83" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="16" pageNumber="83">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="16" pageNumber="83">
<taxonomicName class="Sordariomycetes" genus="Dendrostoma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Dendrostoma qinlingense" order="Diaporthales" pageId="16" pageNumber="83" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="qinlingense">Dendrostoma qinlingense</taxonomicName>
was discovered on two 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Quercus" order="Fagales" pageId="16" pageNumber="83" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Quercus</taxonomicName>
species on the Qinling Mountain in northwest China. This species is phylogenetically related to 
<taxonomicName class="Sordariomycetes" genus="Dendrostoma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Dendrostoma osmanthi" order="Diaporthales" pageId="16" pageNumber="83" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="osmanthi">Dendrostoma osmanthi</taxonomicName>
on 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Oleaceae" genus="Osmanthus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Osmanthus fragrans" order="Lamiales" pageId="16" pageNumber="83" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fragrans">Osmanthus fragrans</taxonomicName>
. However, 
<taxonomicName class="Sordariomycetes" genus="Dendrostoma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Dendrostoma qinlingense" order="Diaporthales" pageId="16" pageNumber="83" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="qinlingense">Dendrostoma qinlingense</taxonomicName>
differs from 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. osmanthi" pageId="16" pageNumber="83" rank="species" species="osmanthi">D. osmanthi</taxonomicName>
by much larger conidia (16-18 
<normalizedToken originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
3.3-3.7 
<normalizedToken originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
in 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. qinlingense" pageId="16" pageNumber="83" rank="species" species="qinlingense">D. qinlingense</taxonomicName>
vs. 7.5-10 
<normalizedToken originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
2-2.5 
<normalizedToken originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
in 
<taxonomicName genus="D." lsidName="D. osmanthi" pageId="16" pageNumber="83" rank="species" species="osmanthi">D. osmanthi</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
